Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:10.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,The Santa I work for is tiny and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm delivering a bunch \Nof presents again this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Let's work hard, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:17.74,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:22.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Heave-ho, heave-ho, heave-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:22.00,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:24.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:26.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Uh, Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I know we're going to be really busy today,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,but let's try not to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:42.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,We'll be efficient and avoid overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:45.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I wasn't reaching out... for a hug...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,but rather offering to carry your packages...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I am so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.29,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Let's do a good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.04,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Mistake or not, she gave me a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:08.41,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,Well, it's Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:11.45,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,so it's probably fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:13.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,R-Right! On my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Happy, merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:25.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,A... A dream?
