Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.33,Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,How did he know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:41.10,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.72,Show_Title,Title sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H292A2F&\bord0}My {\1a&HFF&\bord1\3c&HA183CA&}T{\3c&H000000&}iny {\bord0\1a&H00&}Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:53.80,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We've got an emergency here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.58,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Are you paying attention, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:02.81,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,There's someone other than me \Ndancing around inside of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.06,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I want to talk to her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.10,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I want to touch her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:13.60,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Look, I get it, but for now try to pipe down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.82,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,What in the world am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.57,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,You're right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:25.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And this is the perfect chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.41,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.12,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I'm trapped by that sweet rich taste
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:35.33,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And I don't think I can ever escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.83,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I may as well just sink into it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:38.64,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.43,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It's another day in your dazzling presence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:46.43,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We may never be \Non the same page with this love but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:52.87,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.70,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Wow, look at all those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:13.75,Episode_Title,Eptitle sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(425,525)\pos(38,315)\an1}#06 {\fscx90}I Can't {\c&H8D6ED2&}Re{\c}sist My Instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:13.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorry to ask you to help me sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:16.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not a problem! It's not like I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Besides, I helped you draw it, \Nso of course I'd help you sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.75,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Helping me draw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That was...
