Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:32.98,sign_4975_56_Days_Earlier,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,48)\fscy200}Days Earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.14,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,You look exhausted. Working on your manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.98,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Deadline's the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:37.16,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,And all my friends who usually \Nhelp out are super busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.06,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,That sounds rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.51,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.78,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,You need some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.37,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,M-Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.70,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's not work-related, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.12,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:57.98,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Still... there are certain technical \Nqualifications involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.23,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:04.21,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,This is a template for in-store installations \Nthat the manager drew before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.09,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.27,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What is this, a new game plus for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.10,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,I haven't reincarnated, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.82,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Manager, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.53,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:18.19,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'm gonna upload something to the cloud. \NLet me know when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:19.61,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.74,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,In that case, could you start\Nwith pages 16 to 22?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.04,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.99,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Could you take a look \Nwhen I finish the first page?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.14,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:33.97,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}It might be an 18 plus BL book, \Nbut that scene isn't too sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.87,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad I was able to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.77,Flashback_Italics,Akina,0,0,0,,I'm really impressed, Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.88,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,It's amazing that you can create something \Nso incredible from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.89,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.54,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}I appreciate it, but considering it's 18 plus BL...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.97,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}And with it being a derivative work, \Nit's not exactly from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.15,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,I finished my first page!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.06,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.67,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.35,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.78,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:08.75,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I accidentally asked him \Nto handle a sexy scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:16.04,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Gotta say, that was a lot of fun! \NOur first project together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.29,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Now that this 18 plus BL book is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.42,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,it's the product of our love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.55,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's not exactly wrong, \Nbut could be interpreted in a weird way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.31,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Here's hoping the product \Nof our love sells a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.49,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Maybe that's what I should have \Ntitled the book...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.94,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,Chika-chan! It's been ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.13,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,How've you been? It's been a while \Nsince I've seen you IRL.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.54,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'm pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.19,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It was last summer, \Nright, Haruna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.19,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,And this is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.03,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.52,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,Your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.73,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.83,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I needed some help, and someone \Nfrom work was nice enough to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.54,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,So you work with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.12,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,and he's your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.58,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Why would you assume that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.01,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Oh! On your bag there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Isn't that Hime-chan from {\i1}Kimihime-chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.04,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,You know it?! That's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.22,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I just started watching it \Nafter it was recommended to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.43,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,By my girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.97,sign_4975_56_Days_Earlier,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\move(161,5,130,5)}My girl\N= Girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.98,sign_4975_56_Days_Earlier,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\an7\move(305,20,336,20)\c&H6D41AD&}My{\c&H9377D3&} girl\N{\c&H434544&}= {\c&H8CA36F&}Ch{\c&HC9A97B&}u{\c&H3B3E3A&}m{\c&HA7A19F&}m{\c&H414244&}y
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.58,Main,Haruna,0,0,0,,So he really is your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.23,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I keep telling you, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.98,Main,Announcer (30s; Female),0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Well, everyone, have a good year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}The year's almost over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.87,Sign_Basic,Phone sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs16\c&H413A3E&\shad0\bord0\frz11.18\frx10\fax.1\pos(344.667,292)}Shinozaki Takuma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, we did exchange contact information...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.67,Main,Announcer (30s; male),0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The annual event is being held again this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.45,Main,Announcer (30s; male),0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}and as you can see, there are \Na ton of guests yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I wonder who's calling so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.81,Main,Reporter (20s; female),0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}How did you enjoy the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.56,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Uh, is this for TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.72,Sign_Basic,Phone Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs16\frx2\fry356\bord0\shad0\pos(358,290)\frz16.59}Katase Shiori (Senpai)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:58.05,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Honestly, great! Her BL book \Nhas been a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,S-Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Senpai's calling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Manager, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right... that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did trade contact info!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm such a lucky guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Better answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Uh, hello, this is Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:17.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, I'm at my parents' house right now... \NIt's been kind of busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:21.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Is everything okay? \NI'm sorry for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.61,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you\Nfor everything this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,You did a really great job over the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:42.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Working with you helped me do better, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,No! I feel like I was more \Na nuisance than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:55.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Y'know, when your senpai thanks you, \Nit's okay to think "Wow, I did a great job!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.04,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Wow, I did a great job... then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,There you go! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:06.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, was that one last abuse \Nof authority before the year was over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:11.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hoping she'll continue to abuse \Nher authority in this way next year, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:17.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm really glad you're my kohai, Shinozaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Me, too. I'm glad you're my senpai, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want anyone else...
