Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Well, uh, here's to another year \Nworking together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,R-Right, let's keep up the good work...
