Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,No, no, and where did that even come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.53,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd buy \Nthat cute little getup on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,A-A senpai from work gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.49,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,A senpai from work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Wh-What now?
