Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,W-Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Now, hold on! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:34.32,Main,Yuataka,0,0,0,,I see... so at long last, \Nmy little brother has found a woman.
