Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Enough, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.40,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,His sister never changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.37,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:31.61,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She's always gone crazy \Nover small, cute things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.10,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,May I take her home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.15,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-kun's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:41.87,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.20,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,This is our department's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.68,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Oh, Chika-chan's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.66,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,My brother's boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:53.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Katase-san and Shinozaki-kun \Nare such a great pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:57.53,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,which is evident by how \Nexcellently they work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.54,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Shinozaki-kun's thorough \Nbut over-cautious approach
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.20,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,is an excellent match for Katase-san's \Ndynamic and supportive style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.20,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,On top of their contributions to the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.47,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,they also help set \Na positive tone in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.65,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I'm curious, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.65,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,The name's Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.12,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Yutaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.74,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Do you have any siblings \Nother than Shinozaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.32,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,It's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:27.13,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,How do you feel about... \Nhaving a tiny, cute little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.17,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:33.42,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Ideally, she'd be fluffy, \Nand meow-meow-ey, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:37.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,You realize... you'd get one \Nif your brother marries her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:44.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.18,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Big... sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:51.94,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.83,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Li'l bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.32,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,So, when's the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.80,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,You're both adults, so there shouldn't be \Nany problems in terms of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Did it not occur to you \Nthere are other considerations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.53,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Get Married Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,There's no such beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.10,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,You seriously haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,And you should \Nstop toying with them, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,But come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,My sister can be really rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's good to see you two get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Is that what it looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:41.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,We always tended to like the same things, \Nso we'd end up fighting over stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.62,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,You like the same things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Does that mean, Shinozaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,When it comes to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.49,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.36,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,I get to give a speech at the wedding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.14,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,No, it's me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.39,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,As the groom's sister, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.89,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,I'm both the groom and \Nthe bride's boss. It should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.15,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.74,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,It has to be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.17,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,No, no, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.97,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hard to say whether they get along or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.21,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,So, which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.91,Main,Shinozaki/Shiori,0,0,0,,Which one what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:34.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, does Yutaka-san \Never mess with you, Hayakawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:41.17,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not small or cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.83,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,You seem small and cute to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.40,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Manager... listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.92,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,For favors at the ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.58,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,we can give away these cute plates \Nwith a print of Shiorin on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'm "Shiorin" now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Wait, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.66,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,No one cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.53,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,The trend these days is to have people \Npick from a catalog, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Don't encourage her, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.58,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.84,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Come on, let's all head to the shrine together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Sounds good. I wonder \Nif there'll be food stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.68,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,You want one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.62,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,I sure hope so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.62,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,Wanna put the cat ears on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.30,Main - Top,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.42,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,They're so cute, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.97,Main - Top,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Oh, cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.14,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:55.04,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.52,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:03.74,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And let it slowly spread throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.70,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:13.59,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Where I once had some toast that glittered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:18.09,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,What is it that makes it so satisfying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:22.26,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Almost like magic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:27.34,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I find myself thinking about that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:32.95,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,How the small things can be the most precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.74,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Deep inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:42.14,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It's ever so bittersweet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:47.06,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,"Just being around you is enough"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:51.08,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Becomes my mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.37,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Baby like sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.70,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Baby you're the sugar

